messages.message: ah, Rocket reported a similar issue. We are working on a fix: https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C065EBCMMNU/p1706042294209329

When we open the PDF, it opens a pre-signed URL from S3 to view the file, so the link you have here is the correct behavior. (not sure how to stop the browser warning tho). It's also good to show a "preview" option in the right click menu to open the file as a preview mode (the URL would be `/path/to/file/in/IB?content-disposition=raw` , in case we failed to load the pre-signed URL.
